adblock_interferance_message.message: Adblock (or similar extension) is known to interfere with SmartVideo. Please add this url to adblock whitelist.

buffered_message.message: The video has been buffered as requested and is ready to play.

click_to_chagne_notification_style.message: Click here to change notification style

click_to_enable_for_this_site.message: Click to enable for this site

click_to_go_to_video.message: Click here to go to video

desktop_notification_denied.message: You have denied permission for desktop notification for this site

do_not_switch_to_hd_on_fullscreen.message: Do not switch to HD on fullscreen

dont_play_only_notify.message: Don't play; only notify that video has buffered

enable_full_screen_if_not_provided.message: Enable full screen if not provided

enable_page_action.message: Show loop button on location bar

extension_description.message: Better YouTube experience. Provides 'Smart Buffer' for slow connections; auto loop; buffer preferences; quality selection; and more.

help_auto_play_on_buffer.message: Once the video is buffered to provided percentage, video will either start playing or you will get a notification. Selecting this option will automatically select the 'auto buffer' option.

help_auto_play_on_smart_buffer.message: SmartVideo determines the percentage buffered before it can start playing the video for unrestricted viewing. This calculation is done based on your current download speed.

help_desktop_notification.message: SmartVideo uses individual website's notification permission. Its good thing. You can disable permission for individual websites if you like.

help_desktop_notification_disabled.message: Desktop notifications are not supported on your browser version.

help_embeded_enable.message: Enable SmartVideo extension for embedded videos

help_enable.message: Enable SmartVideo extension on youtube website

help_experimental_quality_for_html5.message: SmartVideo has started supporting quality selection for HTML5 videos; but its only experimental at the moment.

help_hide_popup.message: If you select this option, you will not see popup when you hover mouse over youtube videos. Though other settings will still apply.

help_only_notification.message: Select the checkbox if you want to be notified when the video is buffered instead of playing the video. You can select notification style(s) below.

help_only_notification_disabled.message: No notification style supported on your browser version.

help_save_bandwidth.message: If you select this option, video will not be initialized automatically. This saves bandwidth. Video will only be initialized/loaded when you click on it. Also, other buffering option will apply once the video is loaded. This feature is not available for HTML5 videos.

help_sound_notification_disabled.message: Sound notifications are not supported on your browser version.

help_turn_off_paged_buffering.message: Sometimes YouTube stops buffering videos that are paused. It only buffers videos for few seconds ahead. Select the checkbox to turn off this behavior.

need_to_select_one_quality_for_this.message: We must select one video quality. Either you select some value or it would be defaulted to 'Medium' when the video loads.

no_notification_supported_on_your_browse.message: No notification style supported on your browser version

reload_tabs_for_setting_to_apply.message: Reload individual tab(s) for this setting to apply.

save_bandwidth.message: Save Bandwidth; Do not initialize video until I click

turn_off_paged_buffering.message: Ensure that videos are buffered even if they are paused
